<h2 class="modal_heading">Current Availability by Site and Week</h2>
<p>Below is the current information on availability at all of our summer sites. You may proceed to register a group in any session that has enough open spaces to accommodate your group.</p> Â 
<p>Please call the SSP office (916-488-6441) if you have any questions or special considerations. We will do our best to work with you to get your group registered!</p>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <td></td>
    <% for i in 0..@schedule[:period_count] -1 do %>
        <td><%= @schedule[:period_names][i]%></td>
    <% end %>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  <% s_count = @schedule[:site_count].to_s.to_i %>
  <% for i in 0..s_count - 1 do %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= @schedule[:site_names][i] %></td>
        <% count = @schedule[:period_count].to_s.to_i %>
        <% for j in 0..count - 1 do %>
          <% if @schedule[:session_id_matrix][i][j] > 0 %>
            <% if Session.find(@schedule[:session_id_matrix][i][j]).senior_high? %>
              <td class="senior-high"><%= @schedule[:avail_matrix][i][j].to_s %></td>
            <% else %>
              <td class="junior-high"><%= @schedule[:avail_matrix][i][j].to_s %></td>
            <% end %>
          <% else %>
            <td>-</td>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </tr>
  <% end %>
  <tr>
  </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p>Junior high sessions are highlighted in red.</p>